---
title: Chicken, Bacon, Lettuce and Tomato Burgers with Ranch and Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: We've upped the ante on this classic burger with succulent lean ground chicken, Greek seasoning and a fresh chive ranch sauce. There's never a dull bite in this weeknight winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-poulet-bacon-laitue-tomate-92eadc54.jpg
